1. Donwload apache cassandra 

2.  unzip it and make two copies of conf folder conf and conf3 

3. Go to each copies change cassandra.yml to cassandra2.yml and cassandra3.yml

Make changes to the following the files

1.   cassandra.yml under conf folder 
      name the clustr
      specify the seed node
      Give listeninng adress and rpc folder
      
2.  cassandra-env.sh under conf folder
    change JMX-folder
    
3. log4j properties under conf folder.
  change log4j.appender.R.file address if needed.
4. cassandra.in.sh under bin folder
   make copies of cassandra.in.sh 
5. cassandra under bin folder
  make copies of cassandra and specify the config folder to use

6. sudo if config lo0 alias 127.0.0.2
      
